---
layout: landing.njk
title: Content Pack Overlays | Ionrift Workshop
description: Compendium overlays that extend the free Ionrift modules with recipes, terrain events, loot tables, sound, and curses. One Patreon subscription unlocks the library.
canonical: https://ionrift.cloud/overlays/
ogTitle: Overlays for the table
ogDescription: Recipes, terrain events, loot tables, sound, and curses. One subscription unlocks the library, install from the Patreon Library in Ionrift Library.
ogImage: https://ionrift.cloud/img/packs/_header.jpg
bodyClass: page-overlays
---

{% include "landing/nav.njk" %}

<main class="page-main page-overlays">
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="page-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
            <span>Overlays</span>
        </nav>

        <header class="overlays-hero" style="--overlays-hero-img: url('/img/packs/_header.jpg');">
            <div class="overlays-hero-shade"></div>
            <div class="overlays-hero-inner">
                <div class="section-label">Content packs</div>
                <h1 class="overlays-hero-title">Overlays for the table</h1>
                <p class="overlays-hero-lead">Compendium overlays extend the free modules with recipes, terrain events, loot tables, sound, and curses. They drop straight into the modules you already run. One subscription unlocks the whole library.</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="overlays-how">
            <div class="pack-how">
                <div class="pack-how-step">
                    <span class="pack-how-num">1</span>
                    <a href="{{ site.patreonPackCollectionUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe on Patreon</a>
                </div>
                <div class="pack-how-step">
                    <span class="pack-how-num">2</span>
                    <span>Open the Patreon Library in Ionrift Library</span>
                </div>
                <div class="pack-how-step">
                    <span class="pack-how-num">3</span>
                    <span>Install packs for the modules you run</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="overlays-tier-legend">The badge on each pack shows how to get it. <span class="pack-tier pack-tier--free">Public</span> packs install without a subscription; <span class="pack-tier pack-tier--free">Subscriber</span> needs any Patreon tier; <span class="pack-tier pack-tier--initiate">Initiate</span> and <span class="pack-tier pack-tier--acolyte">Acolyte</span> need that level or higher.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pack-grid pack-grid--full">
{% for pack in packs %}
            <article class="pack-card" style="--module-color: {{ pack.accent }}; --module-icon-color: {{ pack.iconAccent }};">
                <div class="pack-card-media">
                    <img src="{{ pack.image }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
{% if pack.preview %}
                    <span class="pack-flag">Taking shape</span>
{% endif %}
                </div>
                <div class="pack-card-body">
                    <div class="pack-card-top">
                        <h3 class="pack-name">{{ pack.name }}</h3>
                        <span class="pack-tier pack-tier--{{ pack.tier | lower }}">{{ pack.tierLabel }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="pack-desc">{{ pack.description }}</p>
                    <div class="pack-modules">
{% for mod in pack.modules %}
                        <span class="pack-module-tag">{{ mod }}</span>
{% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
{% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="pack-footer">
            <p class="pack-footer-note">More packs ship with module updates. Keep what you install, even if you cancel.</p>
            <a href="{{ site.patreonPackCollectionUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Browse the Patreon library</a>
        </div>

        <p class="page-back">
            <a href="/#packs">&larr; Back to the workshop</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</main>

{% include "landing/footer.njk" %}
